Badour，他是Raimy的男友，他正准备向她求婚。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A female police detective in 2016 discovers she is able to speak via a ham radio with her father (also a detective) who died in 1996. They forge a new relationship while working together on an unresolved murder case but unintended consequences of the &lsquo;butterfly effect&rsquo; wreak havoc in the present day.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class="byrbt_info_clone" data-clone="224713" data-version="SP" style="display:none">\r\n	Powered by Rhilip''s Autoseed</div>\r\n', 'yes'),
